title: Emily Wants to Play Too-CODEX
description:
Emily Wants to Play Too (c) SKH Apps

Release Date: 12/2017 Protection: Discs: 1 Genre: Action

Emily is back with all new scares in Emily Wants to Play Too. It's
about 7pm on Friday and you are headed to your next delivery
destination. You work for Timmy Thom's Fast Sandwiches and tonight
your job is to deliver sandwiches from 4pm to 11pm. Your next stop
is an interesting location. It is some sort of crime research
facility where evidence from crime scenes around town is processed
and stored

For more info go to: http://store.steampowered.com/app/652190/

Extract
Burn or mount the .iso
Run setup.exe and install
Play
